sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Operator as trustyai-service-operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant Job as lmes-job Pod<br/>(lm-evaluation-harness)
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Model as Model Inference Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over User,MLflow: Flow 1: EvalHub Job Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch LMEvalJob CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: LMEvalJob event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job + ConfigMap<br/>(/meta/job.json)
    K8sAPI-->>Job: Pod scheduled & started

    Job->>Job: Read /meta/job.json<br/>(ConfigMap mount)
    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    EvalHub-->>Job: ACK

    Job->>HFHub: Download benchmark datasets<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN (optional)
    HFHub-->>Job: Dataset artifacts
    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: LOADING_DATA<br/>Auth: Bearer Token

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: RUNNING_EVALUATION
    loop For each evaluation prompt batch (up to 128 concurrent)
        Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)<br/>Custom CA bundle supported
        Model-->>Job: Completion response
    end

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: POST_PROCESSING
    Job->>Job: Compute metrics<br/>(scikit-learn, sacrebleu, rouge)

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS
    Job->>OCI: Push result artifacts<br/>Auth: Registry auth
    OCI-->>Job: Push confirmed
    Job->>MLflow: Log metrics & run metadata<br/>Auth: Configurable
    MLflow-->>Job: run_id returned

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: COMPLETED<br/>+ evaluation results<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    EvalHub-->>Job: ACK

    Note over User,MLflow: Flow 2: Offline/Disconnected Evaluation

    Note over Job: Init container pre-populates /test_data from S3/COS
    Job->>Job: Set HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_DATASETS_OFFLINE=1<br/>TRANSFORMERS_OFFLINE=1
    Job->>Job: Load datasets from /test_data<br/>(no network downloads)
    loop Evaluation (offline data, online inference)
        Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Model-->>Job: Completion response
    end
